<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="burn-to-the-ground">burn to the ground</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>全部焚毁：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Many of the wooden houses and bungalows in Pompeii were burned to the ground.
庞贝城的许多木房子和平房都被烧毁了。</p><footer>人教⑥ – 5</footer></div></div>